cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.MA, cs.PL

The paper presents a framework for applying machine-learning algorithms to the verification of Markov decision processes (MDPs), which involves probabilistic reachability and statistical model-checking. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.SY (Systems and Control). The paper also involves mathematical analysis and optimization, which could fall under cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems) and cs.PL (Programming Languages).
